show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/rQanG8
show.description: He gave up his dreams for love, sending his brother away to build the future he couldn’t. Years later, the brother returns a billionaire—but just as long-awaited love finally nears, a ruthless rival rises to snatch it all. A tale of sacrifice, loyalty, and the battle between love, family, and power.
